      tags: ["flex-lay operations","subsea equipment","Guyana","deepwater development"],
      link: "https://www.offshore-energy.biz/mdl-lends-saipem-a-hand-with-flex-lay-prep-for-ops-in-guyana/",
      coords: [-58.8697,4.8604],
